{"tid":2286001,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"突然明白了，唔好再做好好小姐，無人會謝謝你","createTime":"2020-11-14T14:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T03:35:52.000Z","uid":97887,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"422d9d05f97ff1c0a2a5eac657ab2f41ded22ec6","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"做太好，只會比人屌你做得唔夠好<br />\n<br />\n因為你做開，其他人對你期望會黎黎愈高<br />\n<br />\n明白了。做人就唔應該有多餘的仁慈<br />\n<br />\n善良是好，但是要有底線<br />\n<br />\n沒限度的善良只會害死自己"},{"pid":"89b0942703cf221df2250740e7d32d5f058d8c7d","tid":2286001,"uid":302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"而家先知？"},{"pid":"07b72e7da23652a13dd9c7bb440ff080ecc39794","tid":2286001,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"pmed"},{"pid":"7960d69df2f0d3ffd81751c342f785135faa5a68","tid":2286001,"uid":120064,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"善良要睇人<br />\n對住仆街唔可以心軟"},{"pid":"f67af617a40968357d7e893fe75a00ae71069bcb","tid":2286001,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"為什麼要介意珍惜你的人的說話？<br />\n要為愛你的人而活啊"},{"pid":"2b088d288ad6651142027fbf528da84e67a0dda2","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89b0942703cf221df2250740e7d32d5f058d8c7d","tid":2286001,"uid":302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"而家先知？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"尚巴.....我好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過總算釋懷了<br />\n<br />\n痛苦的是失去一個朋友，或者...從沒擁抱過<br />\n<br />\n今晚我會因為佢（女同事）喊最後一次<br />\n<br />\nTmr當無識過佢<br />\n<br />\n只限公事交流"},{"pid":"46e1413f78cf77c25d7c28728bf8069dc5d294eb","tid":2286001,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n諗起你個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fded56d4aee498b15821d87b0623a6de38fad135","tid":2286001,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"52d746f510146a38ae1ce3316c30da3ac74be93a","tid":2286001,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"壞左既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8e770a090954d67ff044de6d87eb92e0afa4d7","tid":2286001,"uid":12909,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"422d9d05f97ff1c0a2a5eac657ab2f41ded22ec6","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"做太好，只會比人屌你做得唔夠好<br />\n<br />\n因為你做開，其他人對你期望會黎黎愈高<br />\n<br />\n明白了。做人就唔應該有多餘的仁慈<br />\n<br />\n善良是好，但是要有底線<br />\n<br />\n沒限度的善良只會害死自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:09:03.000Z","msg":"成日淨係為左他人<br />\n受傷既都係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個社會好多人都恃住人地既好<br />\n就濫用人地既好心<br />\n某d時候真係要識得保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主其實做咩事呀？"},{"pid":"1fe0461ee58da5ed7ea1518b503d6ae2ed562d40","tid":2286001,"uid":163120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"而家覺醒都唔遲<br />\n好人平時幫手做多啲野就會比人覺得老馮<br />\n下次唔做就比人白眼<br />\n反而拒絕開人地, 偶然幫佢地1,2次, 啲仆街先會覺得你好人   啲撚樣人性就係咁  所以幫人都要睇係咩人"},{"pid":"b0aca9c9ccd2db956e43a68e6eb1cebe087f2155","tid":2286001,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3954e9cffffd68609b83408649cadf962d65541","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46e1413f78cf77c25d7c28728bf8069dc5d294eb","tid":2286001,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n諗起你個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:01:04.000Z","msg":"係，昭陽比自己善良所累"},{"pid":"a95ea4b4a26e45d37f87a755a933a95348abd3d6","tid":2286001,"uid":373972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5fd1f528c1280f120733d920cbce80804efc907","tid":2286001,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"淨係對識得珍惜你既人好就夠了"},{"pid":"01f94888a37a9f57f89ff4ec5ddc2380394d89c4","tid":2286001,"uid":244521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"無謂做世界女 好好小姐<br />\n做人要有被討厭的勇氣"},{"pid":"9d2f9e7f7a30092804891e2bff8c0dd3d195981d","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95ea4b4a26e45d37f87a755a933a95348abd3d6","tid":2286001,"uid":373972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"唔係先生，btw，你的名字，我想對你說的話。"},{"pid":"5c66870907c919e07d498cff8fdaa8c6d136176b","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f94888a37a9f57f89ff4ec5ddc2380394d89c4","tid":2286001,"uid":244521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"無謂做世界女 好好小姐<br />\n做人要有被討厭的勇氣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"世界女先好lo<br />\n<br />\n好好小姐係做好多比人屌唔夠<br />\n<br />\n前者係做少少，比多多人感激"},{"pid":"2eabfba2e91680862ccaa7a7c36c9b395a0c675a","tid":2286001,"uid":33041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5c66870907c919e07d498cff8fdaa8c6d136176b","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f94888a37a9f57f89ff4ec5ddc2380394d89c4","tid":2286001,"uid":244521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"無謂做世界女 好好小姐<br />\n做人要有被討厭的勇氣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"世界女先好lo<br />\n<br />\n好好小姐係做好多比人屌唔夠<br />\n<br />\n前者係做少少，比多多人感激"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"冇錯，世界就係咁<br />\n屋企人都係咁話，對開人好就會俾人當你老奉，有一次拒絕人就俾人當你係衰人<br />\n反而平時唔肯幫人，偶爾幫一兩次人哋就會話你好乖好好<br />\n咁我點解平時要咁辛苦幫你哋，對你哋好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36ede9a506388801e0f27b073bc2a787fa9a4b1","tid":2286001,"uid":244521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c66870907c919e07d498cff8fdaa8c6d136176b","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f94888a37a9f57f89ff4ec5ddc2380394d89c4","tid":2286001,"uid":244521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"無謂做世界女 好好小姐<br />\n做人要有被討厭的勇氣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"世界女先好lo<br />\n<br />\n好好小姐係做好多比人屌唔夠<br />\n<br />\n前者係做少少，比多多人感激"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"可能做世界女呢一刻滿足到你<br />\n<br />\n無論你想做世界女又好 做黑面神又好 做好好小姐又好 <br />\n曹操再奸都有朋友 劉備再好都有敵人o:-)<br />\n都冇可能討好全世界人 總係有人唔妥你<br />\n更重要嘅係唔洗太過顧人嘅想法 <br />\n<br />\n我寧願做黑面神仲好 唔使畀人搵笨柒 又唔使特登去討好人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個八婆朋友寸進尺地向我拗免費服務<br />\n我毫不猶豫屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n討厭我呀？ 對我而言毫無損失 殺咗我吖笨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df37b51c689f72138fa4bc1a7b752fb8f1f5e78","tid":2286001,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"善良係，唔祈望有回報就可以。"},{"pid":"549978f07a3d8dd8768d897088e2108853c2b0cb","tid":2286001,"uid":360334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0fe50f343df7bc9448b364592a5b28aa2ef6ae","tid":2286001,"uid":217555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"醒就最好 做好人遷就人<br />\n最後只會被人當應份+自己辛苦"},{"pid":"ee2ad0a41ec52973b6a9fa79ee53e2befc5a8274","tid":2286001,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8df37b51c689f72138fa4bc1a7b752fb8f1f5e78","tid":2286001,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"善良係，唔祈望有回報就可以。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:04:56.000Z","msg":"已經唔係講回報，係做好多比人屌唔夠<br />\n<br />\n人哋做少少就比人讚好好人"},{"pid":"fa2af5cdce785a69f7af0b4d1f30d3f0d0f0ccd0","tid":2286001,"uid":144312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"咪咁傻，職場真係唔好有感情。一有感情就唔可以理性咁分析"}]}